{"tid":1846893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我對依個政府既憎恨程度已經","createTime":"2020-01-27T18:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T20:37:29.000Z","uid":29153,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"08bf13b114e1d873de8a669fe3d06886b4c9640e","tid":1846893,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:54:04.000Z","msg":"到左先所未有咁高，革命無罪 ，造反有理"},{"pid":"4da7bf1c960743ff367fcf7c92e4d43a9e15efe4","tid":1846893,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:54:25.000Z","msg":"我希望大家同我一齊嗌!! 嗌到大陸都一齊嗌!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846888</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>抗疫保命<br />\n推翻政權</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7750439ddb44a1c2397d87daeae8415c3725b9","tid":1846893,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:16:12.000Z","msg":"黎明行動送頭<br />\n港島遊行集會送頭<br />\n深夜整連儂牆送頭<br />\n派傳單都會畀藍絲割肚不了<br />\n<br />\n而家我哋打旗號叫政府封關阻肺炎呀<br />\n民建聯都唔會夠膽出聲反對啦 粉嶺單野政府都hea應啦<br />\n<br />\n另外想問工會過咗咁多個月有幾多人入咗會？<br />\n全民大三罷？<br />\n唔好話無限期啦 就算一日 短期內我都睇唔出我哋有咩條件做得到 到時幾多生化人入咗關？再搞無限期三罷已經遲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為到時已經有唔少香港人奶咗野 咁醫護仲點罷工呀</span><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦送頭<br />\n你話畀我知唔送頭仲可以點"},{"pid":"eb6478b6caa79e9f484b9cbd0ebf482f7504b2eb","tid":1846893,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:17:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b16f0f3e48142dd10c602bac2f2aa4239bfef908","tid":1846893,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T20:25:04.000Z","msg":"想行刺777<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但無方法"},{"pid":"7164a253135382251af9eca2a52720ccc3432cbc","tid":1846893,"uid":135995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b16f0f3e48142dd10c602bac2f2aa4239bfef908","tid":1846893,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T20:25:04.000Z","msg":"想行刺777<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但無方法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T20:31:51.000Z","msg":"中肺炎 衝入去 <br />\n利申中左仲行到一定衝過去吐口水"},{"pid":"cd77477c9168482997897e470b1643192b9b